---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---

<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Lingo7 Realty"
  description="Privacy Policy for the Lingo7 Realty app."
  canonicalUrl="https://lingo7realty.com/privacy/"
  noindex={true}
>
  <section class="legal">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="date">Last updated: June 8, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
    <p>Personal data is controlled by the administration of lingo7realty.com (the "Administration"). By using the Lingo7 Realty app and website (lingo7realty.com, the "Service") — a service for preparing for the Florida Real Estate license exam — you agree to this Policy.</p>

    <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
    <p>Your email (at registration), your selected translation language, your study progress and test results, your device type, your OS and app version, and anonymized analytics data. Payment details are processed by our payment provider — we do not store bank card information.</p>

    <h2>3. Purposes of Processing</h2>
    <p>Operating the Service, processing payments and granting access, providing technical support, and improving the product.</p>

    <h2>4. Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your data. It may be shared with our payment provider (to process payments), with analytics services (in anonymized form), and as required by applicable law.</p>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request, correct, or delete your data, and withdraw your consent to processing — through the app settings or by request at <a href="mailto:support@lingoseven.com" style="color: #34D399; text-decoration: underline;">support@lingoseven.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>6. Miscellaneous</h2>
    <p>Your data is protected by organizational and technical measures. The website may use cookies. The Administration may update this Policy — the current version is available at lingo7realty.com/privacy/.</p>
  </section>
</LegalLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: 120px 40px 80px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .legal h1 {
    font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .legal .date {
    font-size: 14px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 36px 0 16px;
  }
  .legal p, .legal li {
    font-size: 16px; color: #444; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .legal ul {
    padding-left: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .legal li { margin-bottom: 8px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal { padding: 100px 16px 60px; }
    .legal h1 { font-size: 28px; }
    .legal h2 { font-size: 20px; }
    .legal p, .legal li { font-size: 15px; }
  }
</style>
